{
  "id": "RAW_22d12536",
  "title": "CentOS 之死只是开始？IBM 收购红帽的六年，独立早已名存实亡？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMjYzNjkzNw==&mid=2247635140&idx=1&sn=abd8e1e88f32428c4d9f694f71102e48",
  "date": "2026-03-21 00:02:00",
  "author": "dbaplus社群",
  "siteName": "dbaplus社群",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"us-3745001\">\n     <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding:0 5px;\">\n      <div data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"\">\n       <div data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"\">\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"us-4110356\">\n         <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88516\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;word-wrap:break-word !important;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-align:justify;\">\n          <div style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n           <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n            <div data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: -10px 0px;padding: 0px 10px;max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 100%;word-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n             <div hm_fix=\"461:527\" style=\"padding:10px;margin:0px;word-wrap:break-word !important;max-width:100%;border-width:2px;border-color:white;box-sizing:border-box !important;border-style:solid;\">\n              <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #7f7f7f;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: red;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">IBM斥资340亿美元收购红帽，并承诺给予其独立运营的权利。六年过去了，红帽的营收增长了91%，但他们却违背了所有承诺……</span></span></p>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">三百四十亿美元，六年时间。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">一个接一个的承诺被打破。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100151322\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"width: 311px;height: 233px;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"700\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=955536b5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FgiamgWvCHDYa9UzDjSOvKU7v1O6CJgTV1DmGDvbZnPFQsWr1Aedmpcl5Gr2Tf2eSFEq63QnmZwNpiazDhMYUribT8OicLAzqD5tCHuAicXuic6z8g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">IBM 在 2019 年收购了红帽，并明确保证其独立性。\"红帽将继续由 Jim Whitehurst 和红帽现任管理团队领导，\"新闻稿如是说。\"红帽将作为 IBM 内的一个独立部门运营。\"</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">Linux 社区为此欢呼。IBM，并非以利他主义著称，曾承诺让红帽保持其本色。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们早该想到事情并非如此。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n          <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n           <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一、数据揭示了一个不同的故事</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">红帽 2019 年的收入是 34 亿美元。到 2025 年，这个数字达到了 65 亿美元。这意味着六年内增长了 91%。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片来源：作者，2019-2025 年红帽收入增长时间表\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"104\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100151323\" data-ratio=\"0.18346666666666667\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=02ba3d9e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZRcricqeCuaMBtMGvsPomvx5icqibQwWODcaicuXiax3L2cLTyJJWlGDev8deVAVNO8kZKoxEz9JFZoDBqphLsfialWpGJbCGz40Rtc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 5px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">红帽收入增长时间线 2019–2025</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">红帽现在大约占 IBM 总收入的 10%，但占据了 IBM 软件部门近四分之一的份额，而该部门本身又驱动着公司 45% 的业务。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">红帽是 IBM 的增长引擎。没有红帽，IBM 的企业软件故事将分崩离析。这理应赋予红帽巨大的筹码来维持其独立性。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，IBM 正在一点一点地将其吸收。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果您觉得本文分析有价值，请考虑与关心企业级 Linux 未来的同事分享。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n          <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n           <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">二、2025年9月的公告</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年9月，IBM 宣布红帽的后援员工（人力资源、财务、法务、会计）将从 2026 年起划归 IBM。官方说法是：\"简化运营以提高效率\"。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片来源：作者，IBM 随着时间的推移对红帽功能的吸收\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"125\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100151324\" data-ratio=\"0.22\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5fa5fafc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZ0clrBN860AQ1AXyMicG7S98VuD0qziaLImbeJSbMgV9ibGl7z44VibmlkejqCOBd2kb0Xf6VF6iaco5nuQZN0temCy8odIeiaCOfbU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 5px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">IBM 随时间推移吸收红帽职能的情况</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">IBM 公告中令人不寒而栗的限制条件是：工程、产品、销售和市场部门\"目前\"仍保持独立。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我之前见过这种模式。我目睹过被收购时承诺保持自主权的公司，看着这些承诺在三到五年内逐渐被侵蚀，看着原有的文化被母公司官僚体系所消解。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">后援部门的合并从来不是终点。而是终结的开始。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n          <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n           <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">三、IBM 的剧本显而易见</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">以下是企业吸收的运作方式：</span></span></p>\n         <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">收购时承诺保持独立</span>（已完成）</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">保留品牌，更换领导层</span>（Jim Whitehurst 于 2020 年 4 月晋升为 IBM 总裁，后于 2021 年 7 月从 IBM 辞职；Paul Cormier 成为红帽 CEO）</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n         </ul>\n         <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">榨取最大收入</span>（已完成，2025 年达 65 亿美元）</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n         </ul>\n         <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">\"简化运营\"</span>（已完成，2025 年 9 月公告）</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n         </ul>\n         <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">逐步吸收剩余职能</span>（进行中）</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n         </ul>\n         <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">原始身份被抹去</span>（即将发生）</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n         </ul>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">IBM 以前就这么做过。Lotus Notes、Informix、Rational Software。模式如出一辙。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n          <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n           <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">四、CentOS 灾难</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">还记得 CentOS 吗？红帽在 2020 年 12 月将其\"终结\"，就在 IBM 收购后仅 17 个月。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">CentOS 是 RHEL 的免费下游重建版本，公司用来在生产环境中使用而无需支付授权费。红帽（在 IBM 领导下）将 CentOS Linux 转换为 CentOS Stream，这是一个 RHEL 的滚动预览版。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片来源：作者，CentOS 到 RHEL 替代方案决策树\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"110\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100151325\" data-ratio=\"0.19333333333333333\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be8de29d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZbPofadAqAmTARY7orAl5tCv5j8ICZmQ9Wf4iaesz3xeRSAibRPqSo6PfvBRsEwQZ4LIZ8om3mytia7rDsET4WaGL8JCh2zLT9WM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 5px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">CentOS 到 RHEL 替代方案决策树</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">社区并没有默默接受。AlmaLinux 和 Rocky Linux 作为 RHEL 的重建版本出现了。但红帽（IBM）随后在 2023 年 6 月限制了对 RHEL 源代码的访问，使得重建变得更加困难。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">模式很清晰：榨取价值，限制社区访问，最大化收入提取。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这引起了所有目睹过 IBM 收购的人的共鸣。如果您也经历过这种模式，请鼓掌以帮助其他人看到这一点。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n          <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n           <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">五、为什么我不使用 Fedora（即使 Linus 在用）</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fedora 有一个声誉问题。不是关于质量（它其实很稳定），而是关于其目的。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">每一个 Fedora 版本都是 RHEL 的 beta 测试。新特性在 Fedora 用户那里进行测试，通过 CentOS Stream 进行稳定化，然后打包到红帽企业 Linux 中。这是 IBM 年收入 65 亿美元的产品。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个流程很清晰：Fedora（社区测试）到 CentOS Stream（预生产稳定化）到 RHEL（企业利润）。您报告的每一个错误，发现的每一个边缘案例，记录的每一个兼容性问题，都直接流入了 IBM 的商业路线图。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">您是在为一家市值 1650 亿美元的公司提供免费的 QA 劳动力。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">Linus Torvalds 使用 Fedora。他曾多次公开表示过。他从 2008 年开始使用，当时他需要良好的 PowerPC 支持。他的工作流程很简单：安装 Fedora，编译自己的内核，其他一切都能正常工作。他觉得这比 Debian 更实用（安装太麻烦），并且比起 Ubuntu 更偏爱它。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以理解。Linus 是一名内核开发者。他的工作就是让 Linux 更好地为每个人工作，包括商业供应商。围绕发行版的公司政治不是他关心的事，也不应该是。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我的情况不同。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我拒绝做 IBM 的无偿质量保证。我花了 20 多年时间构建系统，调试生产事故，提交详细的错误报告。这项工作是有价值的。当我为一个发行版做贡献时，我希望我的努力能使社区受益，而不是补贴一个公司产品的生产线。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">有一些替代方案不会滋养 IBM 的收入来源。Debian 在 30 多年后仍然保持独立。Arch 让您掌控一切，没有公司议程。openSUSE Tumbleweed 提供由基金会支持的滚动更新，而非对冲基金收购。Void Linux 保持精简和社区驱动。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用任何适合您的发行版。但要明白您正在为什么付出。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">当您运行 Fedora 时，您不仅仅是在使用 Linux。您是在为 IBM 工作，无论您是否知晓。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n          <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n           <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">六、曾经独立的样子</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">在被 IBM 收购之前，红帽拥有：</span></span></p>\n         <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">自己的招聘流程</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">独立的财务报告</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">代表红帽利益的独立法律顾问</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">与开源社区的直接互动</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">吸引人才的文化自主权</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n         </ul>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">在被 IBM 吸收之后：</span></span></p>\n         <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">IBM 的人力资源流程</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">合并后的财务报告</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">IBM 的法律监督</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">经过 IBM 信息筛选后的社区互动</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n           <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">每个剩余独立性前都有的\"目前\"作为限定词</span></span></p>\n          </li>\n         </ul>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">被划归的后援员工不仅仅是行政人员。他们是维持红帽独特文化、处理红帽特定招聘需求、并让公司作为红帽运营的人。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n          <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n           <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">七、替代方案比以往任何时候都重要</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果红帽的独立性让您担忧，以下是可选的路径：</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AlmaLinux：</span>社区驱动，非盈利治理，与 RHEL 二进制兼容的替代方案。永远免费。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Rocky Linux：</span>由 CentOS 联合创始人 Gregory Kurtzer 创立，明确旨在保留 CentOS 的使命。社区控制。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Debian：</span>坚如磐石的基础，没有公司所有权。Ubuntu、Linux Mint 以及数十个发行版都基于 Debian 构建。因为没有公司可被收购，所以没有收购风险。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">SUSE Multi-Linux Support</span>（原 SUSE Liberty Linux）：为 RHEL 工作负载提供企业级支持，而无 IBM 锁定。SUSE 提供商业支持，但不附带 IBM 的依附关系。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片来源：作者，Enterprise Linux 替代方案比较\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"175\" data-backw=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100151326\" data-ratio=\"0.3080289193302892\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"5256\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c297c680&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYa99YKBxUiacX0iaNbhF6B55WgqwHicfwrsjXaV3BC9Dib2wHEK9CyiaH3qFic9OpMpKsslWTO3GIQACQKomX4vW3arz3FJqWlSeAIibo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 5px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">企业级 Linux 替代方案比较</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n          <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n           <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">八、社区的沉默震耳欲聋</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">最让我沮丧的是，在企业级 Linux 社区中，几乎没有什么反对声音。人们将 IBM 吸收红 Hat 视为不可避免，仿佛在 340 亿美元收购中做出的承诺只是营销说辞，没人指望它能兑现。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">多年来，我一直在 RHEL 上设计系统架构。我曾向客户推荐它，因为红帽的工程能力和社区参与是真诚的。这个推荐每年都变得越来越难。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年9月的公告本应是一个重大新闻。然而，它却只得到了极少的报道。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">红帽的声誉建立在开源价值观和社区信任之上。IBM 正在用这种声誉换取季度效率提升。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n          <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n           <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">九、接下来会发生什么</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我的预测：三年内，红帽的工程和产品团队将与 IBM 更广泛的基础设施进行\"整合\"。品牌将保留（IBM 为此支付了 340 亿美元），但独立性将荡然无存。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">红帽将变成 IBM 企业 Linux，只是名称未变而已。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">红帽对 IBM 软件业务的战略重要性（推动着占公司 45% 业务的部门增长）使得 IBM 有充分的动机去榨取最大价值，而不是去保留那些曾让红帽成功的东西。从 IBM 的角度来看，他们已经获得了品牌。现在他们正在优化成本。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果您正在做出长期的企业级 Linux 决策，请将这一发展轨迹纳入您的规划。2019 年的红帽已不复存在。2030 年的红帽可能与今天剩下的模样大相径庭。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">您的组织是否已经开始评估替代方案？您在生产环境中使用 AlmaLinux 或 Rocky Linux 的经验如何？您可以在评论中分享您的观点。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n         <p style=\"padding:0px 0.5em;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: #888888;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者丨Can Artuc &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;编译丨dbaplus社群</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"padding:0px 0.5em;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: #888888;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">来源丨网址：<a href=\"https://canartuc.medium.com/how-ibm-is-destroying-red-hats-independence-the-34-billion-betrayal-b3aed28030aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://canartuc.medium.com/how-ibm-is-destroying-red-hats-independence-the-34-billion-betrayal-b3aed28030aa</a></span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"padding:0px 0.5em;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: #888888;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">*仅为提供参考和学习交流，不代表dbaplus社群立场！dbaplus社群欢迎广大技术人员投稿，投稿邮箱：</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: #888888;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">editor@dbaplus.cn</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度分析了 IBM 收购红帽六年来的整合进程，指出红帽正逐渐丧失独立性，并探讨了其对开源生态及企业级 Linux 选择的影响。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度分析了 IBM 收购红帽六年来的整合进程，指出红帽正逐渐丧失独立性，并探讨了其对开源生态及企业级 Linux 选择的影响。",
  "summary": "文章回顾了 2019 年 IBM 以 340 亿美元收购红帽后的演变历程。尽管最初 IBM 承诺保持红帽的独立运营，但随着红帽营收在六年内增长 91%（2025 年达 65 亿美元）并成为 IBM 软件业务的核心增长引擎，母公司的吸收动作愈发明显。作者详细列举了从 2020 年 CentOS 停更、2023 年限制 RHEL 源码访问，到 2025 年 9 月宣布合并后援部门（人力、财务、法务等）的系列举措，认为这是“终结的开始”。文章还尖锐地指出 Fedora 用户实际上在为 IBM 提供免费 QA 劳动力，并建议担忧红帽未来的企业应积极评估 AlmaLinux、Rocky Linux 和 Debian 等更具独立性的替代方案。最终预测红帽将在三年内被彻底整合，仅保留品牌外壳。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "IBM 正在逐步违背最初的独立性承诺，通过职能合并加速吸收红帽。",
      "explanation": "从 2026 年起，红帽的后援职能将划归 IBM，这标志着其作为独立实体的终结，原有文化正被母公司官僚体系消解。"
    },
    {
      "point": "红帽已成为 IBM 软件业务的财务支柱，这反而加速了母公司对其控制的欲望。",
      "explanation": "红帽贡献了 IBM 软件部门近四分之一的份额，为了榨取最大商业价值，IBM 倾向于优化成本并限制社区免费访问权限。"
    },
    {
      "point": "CentOS 的终结和 RHEL 源码限制是 IBM 商业剧本中“榨取价值”的关键步骤。",
      "explanation": "通过将 CentOS 转换为滚动预览版并限制源码，IBM 迫使企业用户转向付费的 RHEL，从而实现了收入的快速增长。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Fedora 的角色被重新定义为 IBM 商业产品的免费测试场和质量保证工具。",
      "explanation": "Fedora 的新特性测试直接流入 RHEL 商业路线图，开发者在贡献社区的同时，实际上是在无偿补贴 IBM 的生产线。"
